Package: genepicoloc
Title: R Package to Facilitate Genetic (olocalization Analyses
Version: 0.9.3
Date: 2025-08-27
Authors@R: 
    person("Oleg", "Borisov", , "oleg.borisov@uniklinik-freiburg.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8700-4335"))
Description: Provides tools for efficient genetic colocalization analysis
    across multiple QTL (eQTL, pQTL, mQTL) and PheWAS datasets (clinical traits).
    Features scalable pipeline architecture with tar-based storage for
    handling large-scale analyses.
